Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.255 --> 00:00:07.615
 Welcome to this video of the Nespresso Technical Assistance Service on the decalcification of your PIXIE machine. 

00:00:08.005 --> 00:00:16.864
 In order to obtain a perfect cup of coffee at all times, we recommend that you disqualify your PIXIE machine at least once a year. 

00:00:18.754 --> 00:00:24.614
 The Nespresso Club offers you a decalcification kit that has been specially designed for your Nespresso machine. 

00:00:27.253 --> 00:00:30.613
 You will now check how easy it is to decalcify your machine. 

00:00:36.503 --> 00:00:38.612
 Turn on the machine. 

00:00:38.753 --> 00:00:42.362
 Before beginning, do not forget to extract all the capsules. 

00:00:44.003 --> 00:00:46.112
 Empty container of capsules used 

00:00:49.002 --> 00:00:50.362
 and the anti-drip tray. 

00:00:54.502 --> 00:00:58.612
 Place a container of 1 l capacity under the exit of the coffee. 

00:01:00.502 --> 00:01:04.111
 Fill the water tank with 500 ml of water 

00:01:04.251 --> 00:01:06.861
 and Nespresso's decalcification solution. 

00:01:12.500 --> 00:01:16.611
 To activate the decalcification mode, wait until the two buttons stop blinking 

00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:23.860
 and press the two buttons simultaneously for 3 seconds. 

00:01:24.750 --> 00:01:29.610
 The lights will start to blink quickly to indicate that the decalcification cycle is activated. 

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:33.610
 Click the Lungo button to get started. 

00:01:37.500 --> 00:01:42.610
 When the flow has been cut, fill the water tank with the solution used. 

00:01:51.500 --> 00:01:56.860
 Press the Lungo button and let the entire decalcification solution flow through the machine. 

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:09.860
 Finally, empty and rinse the water tank thoroughly. 

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:19.360
 Fill in the water tank with clean water. 

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:31.360
 Press the Lungo button to empty the water tank completely. 

00:02:40.250 --> 00:02:43.360
 Empty and rinse the anti-drip tray. 

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:57.110
 Press the two buttons simultaneously for 3 seconds to exit the decalcification mode. 

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:01.110
 The PIXIE machine is already ready. 

00:03:01.250 --> 00:03:08.860
 Now you can continue to enjoy our range of Grands Crus, designed specifically to optimize the quality of the extraction of your machine 

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:13.860
 and guarantee the highest quality Nespresso coffee, cup after cup. 

